Package: cheopsr
Type: Package
Title: Talking to the Hight Performance CHEOPS Cluster at the University of Cologne
Version: 0.2
Author@R: person("Malte", "Bonart", email = "bonartm@uni-koeln.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Various utility functions to talk to the CHEOPS cluster from within R. Send job files, scripts, data and collect the results. 
  Note that you must have a valid user account from the University of Cologne. This package heaviliy calls the ssh and scp command line programs. 
  So this package can only be used in combination with a common Linux distribution!
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
SystemRequirements: Package only works under a Linux system.
Suggests: testthat
